modules.description: This module runs test suites for functions returning Lwt promises, supporting both synchronous and asynchronous test cases. It integrates with Cmdliner for command-line configuration and executes tests with a switch to manage cancellation. Use it to test MirageOS-compatible libraries with async I/O and CLI-driven setup.
